org.vaniglia.messagequeue.storage
Class MessageStorageParameters

java.lang.Object
  org.vaniglia.messagequeue.storage.MessageStorageParameters
Direct Known Subclasses:
MessageStorageParameters.FileSystemStorageParameters, MessageStorageParameters.JDBCStorageParameters, MessageStorageParameters.MemoryStorageParameters
public abstract class MessageStorageParameters
extends java.lang.Object

This class is a container for parameters used on Message Storage creation. The base (and abstract) class contains static methods to create and initialize the different subtypes that are used for different Message Storage types.
